Text: Looks like the filename got squished a bit. When was this who guest-starred?
It should say Jenna Fischer, but there is a bug that causes the site to mangle the letters "Je" sometimes.

It looks like it hangs up on ".Je" with a leading period.
Take that period out and the error vanishes,

It looks like it hangs up on ". J e" with a leading period.
Take that period out and the error vanishes,

So, It has to be "nine dot J e" (without the spaces)..

Maybe that sequence matches a keyword
or is interpreted as an unprintable character.
Oho!  Putting spaces between the four characters  doesn't help.  That's a pretty odd bug.
